          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><image src="MD-Blend-Curve-Pop.png" scale="100.00%" styleclass="Image Caption"></image></para>
        </td>
        <td style="width:268px;">
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text style="font-weight:normal; font-style:normal;">A </text><text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Blend-Curve</text> is a <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Sketch-Elements">sketch-element</link>. At its <text styleclass="Popup Box2">start-Point</text> and <text styleclass="Popup Box2">end-point</text> you can edit its angle, curvature and curvature rate. </para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box">It is often used to guide <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Motion-Driven-Point">Motion-Points</link>.</para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;"/></para>
          <para styleclass="Popup Box"><text styleclass="VariableName-small">Note</text>: You <text styleclass="VariableName-small" style="color:#ff0000;">cannot</text> add a <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Polyline</text> or <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Profile</text> to a sketch-loop with a <text styleclass="Popup Box-Elements">Blend-Curve</text>.</para>
          <para styleclass="Normal"><line style="height:1px; color:#993300;"/></para>
          <para styleclass="SeeAlso-small">See also: <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Dialog-FunctionBlock-BlendCurve">Blend-Curve</link> dialog-box,  <link displaytype="text" defaultstyle="true" type="topiclink" href="MD-Motion-Path-FB">Motion-Path FB</link></para>
        </td>
      </tr>
